<br>
<br>
The satelite we offer is through direct way/direct pc.  The equipment is $149, and you need a $19 software package.  The service is $39/mo for just the satellite(downstream), if you provide your own dialup acct for the upstream.  Or you can get their dailup which is $10/mo. - so about $50/mo if you go with all their stuff.<br>
